mac_format
======
A simple library for reformatting MAC-addresses.
<br />
<hr>

### How

`````pycon
from mac_formatter import MACFormation

mac_address = '01:ab:02:cd:03:ef'
mac = MACFormation(mac_address)

print(mac.dot)
print(mac.line)
print(mac.space)
print(mac.colon)
`````
output:
`````bash
01ab.02cd.03ef
01-ab-02-cd-03-ef
01 ab 02 cd 03 ef
01:ab:02:cd:03:ef
`````
